N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 175.18 - Use of trade or corporate name

State Regulations

No licensed real estate broker or applicant applying for a
real estate broker's license, may use a trade or corporate name which, in the
opinion of the Department of State, is so similar to the trade name or
corporate name of any licensed real estate broker that confusion to the public
will result therefrom. Notes
